55#include <fdt.h>
56
57#define FDT_ALIGN(x, a) (((x) + (a) - 1) & ~((a) - 1))
58#define FDT_TAGALIGN(x) (FDT_ALIGN((x), FDT_TAGSIZE))
59
60#define FDT_CHECK_HEADER(fdt) \
61 { \
62 int __err; \
63 if ((__err = fdt_check_header(fdt)) != 0) \
64 return __err; \
65 }
66
67int _fdt_check_node_offset(const void *fdt, int offset);
68int _fdt_check_prop_offset(const void *fdt, int offset);
69const char *_fdt_find_string(const char *strtab, int tabsize, const char *s);
70int _fdt_node_end_offset(void *fdt, int nodeoffset);
71
72static inline const void *_fdt_offset_ptr(const void *fdt, int offset)
73{
74 return (const char *)fdt + fdt_off_dt_struct(fdt) + offset;
75}
76
77static inline void *_fdt_offset_ptr_w(void *fdt, int offset)
78{
79 return (void *)(uintptr_t)_fdt_offset_ptr(fdt, offset);
80}
81
82static inline const struct fdt_reserve_entry *_fdt_mem_rsv(const void *fdt, int n)
83{
84 const struct fdt_reserve_entry *rsv_table =
85 (const struct fdt_reserve_entry *)
86 ((const char *)fdt + fdt_off_mem_rsvmap(fdt));
87
88 return rsv_table + n;
89}
90static inline struct fdt_reserve_entry *_fdt_mem_rsv_w(void *fdt, int n)
91{
92 return (void *)(uintptr_t)_fdt_mem_rsv(fdt, n);
93}

95#define FDT_SW_MAGIC (~FDT_MAGIC)
